---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
---

<Layout title="Anuncie no Portal | emguapi.com">
    <Navbar />

    <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 my-16 md:my-24 font-sans">
        
        {/* HEADER */}
        <header class="text-center mb-20 max-w-3xl mx-auto border-b border-gray-200 pb-12">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-sm border border-red-base bg-red-base/5 text-red-base font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-base animate-pulse"></span>
                Espaço Publicitário
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-navy-dark uppercase tracking-tighter leading-tight mb-6">
                Destaque sua <br/>
                <span class="text-red-base">
                    Marca Aqui
                </span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed font-medium">
                Conecte seu negócio com milhares de moradores, turistas e leitores diários de Guapimirim e da Baixada Fluminense.
            </p>
        </header>

        {/* BENEFÍCIOS */}
        <section class="mb-24">
            <h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-black text-navy-dark uppercase tracking-tighter mb-12 flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
                <span class="w-8 h-1.5 bg-red-base inline-block"></span>
                Por que o emguapi.com?
                <span class="w-8 h-1.5 bg-red-base inline-block"></span>
            </h2>
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-navy-base transition-all group">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white rounded-md border border-gray-200 flex items-center justify-center text-red-base mb-6 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform shadow-sm">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-navy-dark mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight">Público Engajado</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm font-medium">Fale diretamente com quem mora, consome e vive o dia a dia da cidade. Anúncio sem desperdício de verba.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-navy-base transition-all group">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white rounded-md border border-gray-200 flex items-center justify-center text-navy-base mb-6 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform shadow-sm">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-navy-dark mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight">Foco no Município</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm font-medium">Somos o portal focado nas demandas reais de Guapimirim. Sua marca associada a um jornalismo útil.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 hover:border-navy-base transition-all group">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white rounded-md border border-gray-200 flex items-center justify-center text-red-base mb-6 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform shadow-sm">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"></polyline></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-navy-dark mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight">Conteúdo Dinâmico</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm font-medium">Notícias diárias, guia de turismo e horários de trens, garantindo acessos recorrentes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        {/* PLANOS / COMO APARECER */}
        <section class="mb-24">
            <div class="bg-navy-dark rounded-lg p-10 md:p-16 text-white shadow-xl relative overflow-hidden border-t-8 border-red-base">
                
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter mb-10 relative z-10 border-b border-white/20 pb-4">
                    Como você quer aparecer?
                </h2>
                
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 relative z-10">
                    
                    <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-md hover:border-white/30 transition-colors">
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-black mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight">Banner Destaque</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-6 font-medium leading-relaxed">Sua arte no topo da página inicial ou no meio das notícias de maior acesso do portal.</p>
                        <span class="inline-block border border-white text-white font-black uppercase text-[10px] tracking-widest py-2 px-4 rounded-sm">Sob consulta</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-md hover:border-white/30 transition-colors">
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-black mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight">Publieditorial</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-6 font-medium leading-relaxed">Uma matéria completa escrita de forma jornalística sobre o seu negócio ou lançamento.</p>
                        <span class="inline-block border border-white text-white font-black uppercase text-[10px] tracking-widest py-2 px-4 rounded-sm">Sob consulta</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-red-base p-6 rounded-md relative overflow-hidden shadow-lg border border-red-700">
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-black mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight relative z-10">Guia Local</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-white/90 mb-6 font-medium leading-relaxed relative z-10">Cadastro do seu negócio no nosso diretório de classificados e serviços.</p>
                        <span class="inline-block bg-navy-dark text-white font-black uppercase text-[10px] tracking-widest py-2 px-4 rounded-sm relative z-10 shadow-sm">100% Grátis*</span>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        {/* CHAMADA PARA AÇÃO (CTA) */}
        <section class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto border-t border-gray-200 pt-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-navy-dark mb-8">Pronto para aumentar suas vendas?</h2>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
                <a 
                    href="https://wa.me/5521969400053?text=Olá!%20Tenho%20interesse%20em%20anunciar%20no%20portal%20emguapi.com" 
                    target="_blank"
                    class="w-full sm:w-auto flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-[#25D366] text-white font-black uppercase px-8 py-4 rounded-md hover:bg-[#20bd5a] transition-all shadow-md tracking-widest text-xs"
                >
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path></svg>
                    Falar no WhatsApp
                </a>
                <a 
                    href="mailto:anuncie@emguapi.com?subject=Quero%20anunciar%20no%20emguapi.com" 
                    class="w-full sm:w-auto flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-gray-100 text-navy-dark font-black uppercase px-8 py-4 rounded-md border border-gray-200 hover:border-navy-base transition-all tracking-widest text-xs"
                >
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline></svg>
                    Enviar E-mail
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 uppercase mt-8 font-bold tracking-widest text-center">
                *O cadastro no Guia de Classificados é gratuito para empreendedores locais, mediante curadoria da nossa redação.
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>